<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1) Ya Yesunmu, ka ba mu Ruhunka
 Ku dattiɓai ku aikinsa,
 Ku samari ku yi ta shelarsa
 Wanda ya bi Yesu, tsira za ya yi,
 Muna murna har yau zu mu yi
 Alleluya, Amin, Alleluya, Amin,
 Alleluya, Amin.

[V2]
 2) Yesu yana zuwa, za ya karɓe mu.
 Abin da ka shibka, za ka girbe shi
 Idan ka yanke rumbuna, za ka kai
 Zinariya ce, ko azurfa ce, ko itace ne
 Ko ciyawa ce,
 Mmm, babban kuka, rana ta hume ka.
 Mmm, ka ji kumya, rana ta hume ka.

[V3]
 3) Ku masu bi, Almasihu
 Ku duba kwatamci,
 Akan budurwai, goma,
 Biyar, masu azanci
 Suna cewa, ina ango?
 Ni ban san ku ba, in ji Yesu,
 Ni ban san ku ba, ku rabu da ni
 Ni ban san ku ba, in ji Yesu.
 Halleluya, Amin, Halleluya, Amin
 Halleluya Amin.</lyrics>
<title>Ya Yesunmu, Ka Ba Mu Ruhunka LW553</title>
<hymn_number>553</hymn_number>
</song>